subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: Gasquet, the No. 21 seed, smashed his racket on a chair and then went on to earn a place in the quarterfinals with a 7-5, 6-1, 6-7 (7), 7-6 (6) victory over the 26th-seeded Kyrgios.
